Package: proxmox-redfish
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-requests, python3-cryptography
Recommends: python3-virt-firmware, openssl
Maintainer: Jay Binks <jaybinks@gmail.com>
Description: Redfish API daemon for Proxmox VE
 Exposes a DMTF Redfish API in front of Proxmox VE virtual machines, including
 power control, virtual media, boot configuration, and UEFI Secure Boot key
 management. Built for bare-metal provisioning tools (Metal3, OpenStack Ironic,
 OpenShift ZTP, sushy). Validated against the DMTF Redfish-Service-Validator.
 Runs on the system python3 with its two pure-Python dependencies bundled; no
 venv, no pip, no network required at install.
